Catkin Sphinx plugins for cmake domain and ShLexer

Using
-----

To use this plugin, add the following to your ``conf.py``:

    extensions = extensions + ['catkin_sphinx.cmake', 'catkin_sphinx.ShLexer']


ros-theme
---------

copy the content of theme/ros-theme directory to ~/sphinx/ros-theme to work with projects
that require ros-theme.

ros-theme-enabled projects use the following html_theme_path setting:

html_theme_path = [os.path.join(os.path.expanduser('~'), 'sphinx'), 'themes']
